{"tid":492016,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"意外收穫    拼音打字進步神速","createTime":"2017-12-07T05:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T08:12:17.000Z","uid":34676,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"47336fff5fa3dd57482e772a5b8ef9a669ae5c73","tid":492016,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/hongkong/text/2017/0816/105425.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fhongkong%2Ftext%2F2017%2F0816%2F105425.html&d=XFwM8SeD6i6b6mmQRHAgMfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=81e00d03\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/hongkong/text/2017/0816/105425.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.takungpao.com/2017/0816/20170816031526159.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.takungpao.com%2F2017%2F0816%2F20170816031526159.jpg&h=590be625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖：王綽渝表示，若有機會願意到上海發展<br />\n<br />\n　　「在這裏實習過程中，我體會了好多，最有意思的是，我的拼音打字有了不小的進步。」來自香港大學的王綽渝笑着說道。<br />\n<br />\n　　讀經濟金融學系的王綽渝，此次在上海一家融資租賃公司的風險控制部實習。在本職工作做的不錯的同時，王綽渝最大的收穫竟是「打字」速度得到了較大的提高。由於不熟悉拼音，「以前一分鐘能打10個字吧」，不過在練習之後，「現在一分鐘能打20甚至30個，也算是意外的收穫。」<br />\n<br />\n　　王綽渝直言，「我今後也想找金融方面的工作，此次實習對於我日後的發展很有幫助。」學習融資租賃具體業務、與客戶打交道、學習對話技巧&hellip;&hellip;「這些都是非常寶貴的經驗。」而在實習過程中，王綽渝與滬青還結下了深深情誼。「一位同事特地帶我和她家人一起用餐，真的好窩心，很感動，如果有機會，我想我也會來上海發展，很希望再來看一看。」"},{"pid":"eefd01e2670f063ccdf7fc973d7a22eda9c058c7","tid":492016,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:55:23.000Z","msg":"好有用喎"},{"pid":"907b5680e3f58d504fa353cb589b5beb6333b918","tid":492016,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好有用喎</blockquote><br />\n你好<br />\n打Nh已經得<br />\n方便快捷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c0b528857d6dbe37143ee037454a240828d13d","tid":492016,"uid":149778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T06:54:20.000Z","msg":"一分鐘打2~30個字<br />\n佢得一隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b3123c96e46116428d67bd5f0fcc2235f539eb","tid":492016,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T06:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一分鐘打2~30個字<br />\n佢得一隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地又唔係做秘書、打字員，要咁快托咩？"},{"pid":"d1c0c555a32dd450600106423da03589ea0aa1de","tid":492016,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T07:01:04.000Z","msg":"拼音打字熟左係快過速成倉頡<br />\n揀字都免了就更快<br />\n我都係中意倉頡輸入法多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b4fc3811580c14082eddf350384550be65c998","tid":492016,"uid":55568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拼音打字熟左係快過速成倉頡<br />\n揀字都免了就更快<br />\n我都係中意倉頡輸入法多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係邊一種輸入法會快d<br />\n而係所有輸入法都係練得多就會快<br />\n無話用邊種練邊種特別快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}